sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant VIEW as View
    participant SER as Serializer
    participant SVC as Service
    participant SEL as Selector
    participant DB as Database

    FE->>VIEW: request
    VIEW->>SER: validate / shape
    VIEW->>SVC: orchestrate workflow
    SVC->>SEL: read deterministic data when needed
    SVC->>DB: write within transaction when needed
    SEL->>DB: org-scoped reads
    VIEW-->>FE: serializer-ready response
